high_descs: Go toward the door, then turn right to face the black table.
Pick up the mug on the back left corner of the black table.
Turn around, go straight, then turn left to approach the oven.
Heat the mug in the microwave, above the oven.
Turn around, then go straight, then turn left to approach the coffee maker.
Put the mug at the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm mug at the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the small black table.
Pick up the white mug from the table.
Turn right and go to the mmicrowave.
Heat the mug and pick it up again.
Turn around and go to the coffee maker.
Put the mug on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed mug on the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn to the right to see the black table.
Move a step toward the black table and pick up the mug in the back.
Turn around and take the mug to the left, and find the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the mug inside. Turn on the microwave. Open the door and remove the mug, then shut the door.
Take the mug and turn around. Turn left to find the coffee machine.
Place the cup on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Heat a cup and place it under the coffee maker.
